  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"r3KU2G1R\">………X染色体上很多都是维持生命必备的基因。女性两条X染色体有一条是不表达的，会变成<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=14296293&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%B7%B4%E6%B0%8F%E5%B0%8F%E4%BD%93&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">巴氏小体<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>，这个东西在性别检测里特别有用。</p><p data-pid=\"ZPMz5MfR\">男性的Y染色体上则是很多男性性状表达的基因。</p><p data-pid=\"dguZ3iCo\">题外话：</p><p data-pid=\"UdDVWT-q\">染色体数目异常是一种<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=14296293&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E9%81%97%E4%BC%A0%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">遗传疾病<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>。</p><p data-pid=\"AzmUdWAl\">我们可以见到</p><p data-pid=\"505nIPKQ\">一个X的小姑娘</p><p da